---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/ui/CTASection.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/ui/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import TestimonialsSection from '../../components/sections/TestimonialsSection.astro';

const city = "Hasbrouck Heights";
const title = "CPA in Hasbrouck Heights NJ | ProAxis Tax & Accounting Services";
const description = "ProAxis Tax & Accounting Services is based in Hasbrouck Heights NJ. We're your local CPA — tax preparation, tax planning, bookkeeping, and business advisory for Hasbrouck Heights and surrounding Bergen County communities.";
const canonical = "/service-areas/hasbrouck-heights/";
const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: "Service Areas", url: "/service-areas/" },
  { name: city }
];
const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": ["LocalBusiness", "AccountingService"],
  "name": "ProAxis Tax & Accounting Services",
  "telephone": "+12018002330",
  "email": "info@proaxiscpa.com",
  "url": "https://proaxiscpa.com",
  "address": {
    "@type": "PostalAddress",
    "addressLocality": "Hasbrouck Heights",
    "addressRegion": "NJ",
    "postalCode": "07604",
    "addressCountry": "US"
  },
  "areaServed": { "@type": "City", "name": "Hasbrouck Heights, NJ" }
};
---

<BaseLayout {title} {description} {canonical} {schema} {breadcrumbs}>
  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbs} />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1C1C1E 0%, #2E75B6 100%);" class="py-14 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold mb-4" style="background-color: rgba(197,165,90,0.2); color: #C5A55A;">
        ProAxis Home Base &bull; {city}, NJ &bull; 100% Virtual
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold font-heading text-white mb-4">CPA &amp; Accounting Services in {city}, NJ — Home of ProAxis</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8">ProAxis Tax &amp; Accounting Services is proudly headquartered in Hasbrouck Heights. We're not just serving the Heights — we ARE the Heights. Expert tax preparation, tax planning, and business accounting for our home community.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-white" style="background-color: #22C55E;">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
        <a href="tel:+12018002330" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-white border-2 border-white/40">Call (201) 800-2330</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 lg:py-16">

    <!-- Home base callout -->
    <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 mb-10 border-2" style="border-color: #C5A55A; background-color: rgba(197,165,90,0.06);">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background-color: #C5A55A;">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold font-heading mb-2" style="color: #1C1C1E;">We're a Hasbrouck Heights Business</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700">ProAxis Tax &amp; Accounting Services is based right here in Hasbrouck Heights, NJ 07604. When you work with ProAxis, you're supporting a local Bergen County business that understands this community from the inside — not a distant firm that's never been to the Heights.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Hasbrouck Heights — Our Home Borough</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Hasbrouck Heights is a small but vibrantly self-contained borough in the southern tier of Bergen County. Incorporated in 1894, the Heights has developed a distinct community identity built around its walkable downtown, tight-knit residential neighborhoods, strong school system, and strategic location at the crossroads of some of northern New Jersey's most important commercial corridors. The borough's Main Street district offers an independent retail and dining scene — hardware stores, barbershops, diners, specialty food shops, and professional offices — that keeps residents connected to their community in a way that larger, more suburban municipalities often lose.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">One of the most significant economic anchors in the immediate Hasbrouck Heights area is Teterboro Airport. Located just minutes from the borough, Teterboro is one of the busiest general aviation airports in the United States, handling corporate jets, charter flights, cargo operations, and aviation maintenance businesses. The airport supports a substantial ecosystem of aviation-adjacent businesses based in and around Hasbrouck Heights: aviation fuel suppliers, aircraft maintenance and repair organizations (MROs), charter aviation brokers, aviation security firms, avionics technology companies, and the pilots, mechanics, and aviation professionals who support flight operations. These businesses have unique accounting considerations — aviation equipment depreciation schedules are specialized, FAA maintenance and compliance costs are substantial deductibles, and the revenue recognition models for charter operations differ meaningfully from standard service business accounting.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The Route 17 commercial corridor runs close to the Heights, bringing with it a concentration of auto-related businesses, service stations, light industrial operations, warehousing, and logistics companies. The proximity to the NJ Turnpike and Route 3 makes the immediate area attractive for distribution and light manufacturing operations. These businesses — whether small owner-operated service shops or larger logistics operations — need solid bookkeeping systems that accurately capture inventory, cost of goods sold, vehicle expenses, and payroll, often across both NJ and multistate operations.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The Meadowlands complex — MetLife Stadium, the Meadowlands Racetrack, American Dream mall, and the surrounding commercial development — is a short drive from Hasbrouck Heights and represents one of the major economic engines of the entire region. Businesses serving the Meadowlands event economy — caterers, staffing agencies, transportation companies, security firms, merchandise suppliers — are often based in the southern Bergen County and eastern Bergen County communities, including the Heights area.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">Neighboring communities including Wood-Ridge, Lodi, Moonachie, Little Ferry, South Hackensack, and Rochelle Park share the southern Bergen County character and economic profile. Business owners from these neighboring boroughs frequently turn to Hasbrouck Heights-based professional services firms for tax and accounting help, and ProAxis is proud to serve businesses and families throughout this southern Bergen County corridor.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Tax &amp; Accounting Needs in Hasbrouck Heights</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The local business community in and around Hasbrouck Heights spans a range of industries, and the tax and accounting needs vary accordingly:</p>
    <ul class="list-none space-y-3 mb-6">
      {[
        { heading: "Aviation and airport-adjacent businesses", text: "Teterboro Airport creates a unique cluster of businesses with specialized accounting needs: aircraft depreciation, FAA-mandated maintenance cost tracking, charter revenue recognition, and in some cases, aircraft leasing structures that have distinct tax treatment." },
        { heading: "Route 17 and logistics businesses", text: "Service stations, auto repair shops, fleet operations, and light industrial businesses need clean bookkeeping systems that properly track inventory, vehicle expenses, and the mix of taxable and exempt goods and services for NJ sales tax purposes." },
        { heading: "Small business owner tax planning", text: "Many Hasbrouck Heights residents are small business owners operating in the borough or nearby. S-Corp elections, retirement plan contributions, home office deductions for hybrid workers, and vehicle mileage tracking are recurring planning opportunities." },
        { heading: "Residential homeowner tax strategy", text: "Hasbrouck Heights homeowners, like all Bergen County residents, face significant NJ property taxes. Ensuring that all eligible deductions are captured — mortgage interest, property taxes within the SALT cap, charitable contributions — requires careful return preparation." },
        { heading: "NJ payroll compliance", text: "The NJ Department of Labor takes payroll compliance seriously. Proper worker classification, NJ Earned Sick Leave compliance, UI/TDI/FLI withholding, and annual W-2 and 1099 filing are non-negotiable requirements that a good CPA keeps in order." },
      ].map((item) => (
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg" style="background-color: #F7F8FA;">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0" style="background-color: #C5A55A;"></div>
          <div><span class="font-semibold" style="color: #1C1C1E;">{item.heading}:</span> <span class="text-gray-700">{item.text}</span></div>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>

    <!-- ProAxis Services -->
    <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 mb-10" style="background-color: #F7F8FA;">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">ProAxis Serves Hasbrouck Heights Businesses &amp; Residents</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">This is home. ProAxis Tax &amp; Accounting Services was built to serve Bergen County businesses and residents, and Hasbrouck Heights is where we planted our flag. Whether you're a Main Street retailer, an aviation-adjacent business near Teterboro, a Route 17 service business, or a Heights homeowner who wants expert NJ tax preparation, ProAxis is your CPA team.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-5">Our fully virtual delivery model means you get personalized, responsive CPA service without ever having to leave the Heights — your documents travel digitally, your consultations happen on video, and your questions get answered quickly by a team that knows your community.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        {[
          { name: "Tax Preparation", link: "/tax-services/tax-preparation/" },
          { name: "Tax Planning", link: "/tax-services/tax-planning/" },
          { name: "Bookkeeping", link: "/business-services/bookkeeping/" },
          { name: "Business Advisory", link: "/business-services/" },
          { name: "NJ SALT Consulting", link: "/tax-services/nj-salt-consulting/" },
          { name: "Fractional CFO", link: "/business-services/fractional-cfo/" },
        ].map((svc) => (
          <a href={svc.link} class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-white border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 font-medium transition-all" style="color: #2E75B6;">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
            {svc.name}
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Nearby Areas We Also Serve</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">In addition to Hasbrouck Heights, ProAxis serves businesses and residents throughout the southern Bergen County corridor and all of Bergen County:</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-8">
      {[
        { name: "Rutherford", slug: "rutherford" },
        { name: "Garfield", slug: "garfield" },
        { name: "Hackensack", slug: "hackensack" },
        { name: "Bergen County (all)", slug: "bergen-county" },
      ].map((area) => (
        <a href={`/service-areas/${area.slug}/`} class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border hover:shadow-sm transition-all" style="border-color: #2E75B6; color: #2E75B6; background-color: rgba(46,117,182,0.05);">{area.name}</a>
      ))}
    </div>
    <p class="text-gray-700">Ready to get started with your hometown CPA? <a href="/contact/" class="font-medium underline" style="color: #2E75B6;">Schedule a free consultation</a> with ProAxis today, or call us directly at <a href="tel:+12018002330" class="font-medium underline" style="color: #2E75B6;">(201) 800-2330</a>.</p>
  </article>

  <TestimonialsSection />
  <CTASection heading={"Your Hasbrouck Heights CPA — Schedule Your Free Consultation Today"} />
</BaseLayout>
